656
00:43:28,314 --> 00:43:31,233
Ah…

657
00:43:31,234 --> 00:43:34,820
Mengingat usia Anda, saya sarankan
dirawat di rumah sakit beberapa hari sebelumnya

658
00:43:34,821 --> 00:43:36,404
