885
00:55:34,957 --> 00:55:38,709
Apakah dia pergi ke rumah sakit?

886
00:55:38,710 --> 00:55:39,919
Tidak, dia bilang dia harus mampir ke suatu tempat.

887
00:55:39,920 --> 00:55:42,505
Dia harus mengembalikan sesuatu kepada seseorang.

888
00:55:42,506 --> 00:55:46,300
Oh…

889
00:55:46,301 --> 00:55:47,718
